sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner as Org Owner/Manager
    actor Member
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Email as Resend Email

    Owner->>Browser: Dashboard sidebar → "Members"
    Browser->>API: GET /api/organizations/{orgId}/members
    API->>DB: OrganizationMember.findMany(orgId)
    API-->>Browser: Members with roles

    Owner->>Browser: Use role dropdown next to member name
    Browser->>API: PATCH /api/organizations/{orgId}/members
    Note right of Browser: { memberId, role: "MANAGER" }
    API->>DB: OrganizationMember.update(role)
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Owner->>Browser: Click remove on member entry
    Browser->>API: DELETE /api/organizations/{orgId}/members
    API->>DB: OrganizationMember.delete(memberId)
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Member->>Browser: Click "Contact Owner" on organization card
    Browser->>API: POST /api/organizations/{orgId}/contact
    Note right of Browser: { message }
    API->>DB: Find org OWNER's email
    API->>Email: sendOrgContactEmail(owner, sender, message)
    Email-->>Owner: Contact message with reply-to
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
